-They're not real delinquents!

170
00:10:32,465 --> 00:10:34,717
<i>Oh good. They seem alright.</i>

171
00:10:35,426 --> 00:10:39,722
<i>Now, who were they standing around?</i>

172
00:10:44,852 --> 00:10:46,062
