176
00:10:52,777 --> 00:10:55,446
<i>She's looking! At me!</i>

177
00:10:55,529 --> 00:10:57,365
<i>Why is she staring so much?</i>

178
00:10:57,448 --> 00:10:59,075
<i>I'm scared!</i>

179
00:10:59,158 --> 00:11:01,827
<i>My knees are weak.</i>

180
00:11:01,911 --> 00:11:03,496
He sat down!

181
00:11:03,579 --> 00:11:06,457
<i>Deep breaths, deep breaths!</i>

182
00:11:06,540 --> 00:11:08,417
EXHALE

183
00:11:13,422 --> 00:11:15,424
-<i>She's still staring!</i>
-TOO SCARED TO MOVE

184
00:11:15,508 --> 00:11:19,095
<i>Everyone usually looks away</i>
<i>when I meet their gaze.</i>

185
00:11:19,178 --> 00:11:24,266
<i>But this might be the first time</i>
<i>someone looked me in the eyes.</i>

186
00:11:24,809 --> 00:11:26,060
<i>Oh, right!</i>

187
00:11:26,143 --> 00:11:29,271
Even Monkeys Can Talk <i>chapter 4, page 116!</i>

188
00:11:29,355 --> 00:11:32,566
<i>"Get your feelings across</i>
<i>by looking people in the eyes!"</i>

189
00:11:32,650 --> 00:11:35,778
<i>That's why this person</i>
<i>is looking me in the eyes!</i>

190
00:11:35,861 --> 00:11:39,615
<i>It means she wants to communicate, right?</i>

191
00:11:40,408 --> 00:11:42,618
