00:11:54,922 --> 00:11:56,048
Uh.

197
00:11:56,632 --> 00:11:59,218
Um, you're Katai. Aren't you?

198
00:11:59,718 --> 00:12:00,636
Huh?

199
00:12:00,719 --> 00:12:02,680
<i>Aaah! No!</i>

200
00:12:02,763 --> 00:12:05,224
<i>My voice changed and now it's super low.</i>

201
00:12:05,307 --> 00:12:09,353
<i>If I don't make it higher,</i>
<i>I sound like I'm really mad!</i>

202
00:12:11,063 --> 00:12:13,691
<i>Now he thinks I'm a jerk.</i>

203
00:12:14,400 --> 00:12:17,820
You were out of school
for a long time, right?

204
00:12:18,362 --> 00:12:21,282
