208
00:12:45,598 --> 00:12:46,765
<i>W-Wow.</i>

209
00:12:47,349 --> 00:12:49,810
-<i>This is the power of eye contact.</i>
-STARE

210
00:12:49,894 --> 00:12:51,270
-Here is the library.
-LIBRARY

211
00:12:51,353 --> 00:12:55,983
<i>Walking through the school,</i>
<i>just the two of us.</i>

212
00:12:56,066 --> 00:12:57,860
<i>We're like real friends!</i>

213
00:12:57,943 --> 00:12:59,111
